{"tid":557765,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［遊記］我在俄羅斯的三十天","createTime":"2018-02-11T16:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T14:03:31.000Z","uid":89417,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"813b4e516f72e705a77b4014c9f6bfd1ebef141b","tid":557765,"uid":89417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T16:00:14.000Z","msg":"每年冬天，我都會孭住個backpack去旅行。今年，我選擇踏足俄羅斯。因為網上好少講關於俄羅斯同西伯利亞鐵路既遊記，所以呢，今次我出post會由準備功夫（例如visa)開始講起，如果你準備想/會去，有咩想問，我盡量答你地啦。<br />\n<br />\n首先大概講下我呢30日到底去左邊度，香港&gt;海參崴&gt;伊爾庫次克（貝加爾湖）&gt;新西伯利亞&gt;莫曼斯克&gt;莫斯科&gt;聖彼得堡&gt;香港<br />\n<br />\n去完俄羅斯，我覺得95%既俄羅人都係好人（會西住臉咁幫你），4%係怪人，仲有1%係痴線佬，好彩，我全部都遇到...<br />\n<br />\n認真！如果你係自己一個女仔，勸你唔好搭火車，唔好住airbnb 同埋 共宿既hostel! 最好就梗係有朋友同你一齊去。"},{"pid":"280440655f41e45f2ec7bc41cf7beb96af0fa9ce","tid":557765,"uid":89417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T16:38:54.000Z","msg":"【visa篇】<br />\n如果你去俄羅斯少過14日，咁你可以飛左呢一part! 但係記住記住記住！14日係由你入境果日開始計起，到係離境果日，例如你1號入境，你14號凌晨12點前一定要離境！如果唔係，就要中國大使館打救你！ 有個唔想apply visa, 都有另一個方法留超過14日，就係出境再入境，就會重新計14日，你可以選擇去外蒙或者芬蘭。<br />\n<br />\n咁講番visa先，最麻煩之處就係張invitation letter, 一定要由俄羅斯旅行社/酒店發出，我果時就係Real russia申請既<br />\n<a href=\"https://visas.realrussia.co.uk/Apply/Support_apply2.asp?option=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvisas.realrussia.co.uk%2FApply%2FSupport_apply2.asp%3Foption%3D0&d=cTbfhFij%2FhRN8MJ5IHlsRRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=1de8f402\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://visas.realrussia.co.uk/Apply/Support_apply2.asp?option=0</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/003133_8d898498f0856f91e6e70942790c8e3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F003133_8d898498f0856f91e6e70942790c8e3d.jpg&h=98ecee2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後到details about your visit to russia, 你就揀你會去既城市，最多5個，如果你去超過5個城市，就揀留得較耐既城市，之後係hotel果格呢，雖然佢選擇好多，但係未必係你住果間。所以，<a href=\"http://我建議你係booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%88%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E4%BD%A0%E4%BF%82booking.com&d=cTbfhFij%2FhRN8MJ5IHlsRRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=ba4a76c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">我建議你係booking.com</a>搵番佢有既酒店，你係可以鳩book既，總之就揀d可以免費cancel果種，到你真係拎到visa就可以cancel, 到時你想住airbnb又好，訓街又好，你鐘意啦！出入境時間唔好填錯，錯左就冇左GBP15嫁喇！<br />\n<br />\n然後你就會收到佢既email, 距離申請visa又近左一大步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae83252605341a4dbebe2efca41c072c41bf87a5","tid":557765,"uid":88988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T16:52:12.000Z","msg":"留名幫樓主推"},{"pid":"b07e859f2703ffdfbbbce04f41aa6651eafcf484","tid":557765,"uid":140793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T16:58:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大概用咗幾多錢"},{"pid":"e423f78dcd7671534f8afe26b18e7d81e9a9f120","tid":557765,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:03:23.000Z","msg":"Lm 7月去莫"},{"pid":"da8471aa34f9dd2497fe5595d6af19123ab3542e","tid":557765,"uid":89417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:07:21.000Z","msg":"【visa篇】<br />\n當你係email收到封invitation letter, 就可以上呢個網申請visa<br />\n<a href=\"https://visa.kdmid.ru/PetitionChoice.aspx?AspxAutoDetectCookieSupport=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvisa.kdmid.ru%2FPetitionChoice.aspx%3FAspxAutoDetectCookieSupport%3D1&d=cTbfhFij%2FhRN8MJ5IHlsRRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=d4b9abb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://visa.kdmid.ru/PetitionChoice.aspx?AspxAutoDetectCookieSupport=1</a><br />\n(題外話：以前上網啲人話要hard copy，要由俄羅斯寄番黎香港，郵費超級貴，但係記住！依家係soft copy都得嫁喇！唔好on99比錢寄張垃圾番黎）<br />\n<br />\nCountry 係冇香港嫁，要揀china<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記住個application ID, 唔需要一次過填曬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/005245_2a55978d39c867f239d26e6630d8ddb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F005245_2a55978d39c867f239d26e6630d8ddb6.jpg&h=0d48d2e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/005247_630a8ff4633bcc212da3072f3c1a8e66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F005247_630a8ff4633bcc212da3072f3c1a8e66.jpg&h=cc26b6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有問你有冇朋友係俄羅斯果啲，全部none就可以<br />\n！！！重點黎喇！！！佢話問你想係邊度拎證，記得記得要揀consulate general of the russian federation in hong kong! 因為visa application center係會另收200幾蚊手續費同啲職員好麻煩，2個地方都係相隔一條走廊咋！<br />\n<br />\n然後就去影印同影證件相喇，搞點曬就可以book埋交申請表既appointment<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/010218_0cb7c98b762df488d0ce129cf1487eb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F010218_0cb7c98b762df488d0ce129cf1487eb9.jpg&h=9b315c89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後就print埋invitation letter同埋準備548蚊。大使館係新鴻基中心21樓，一出lift就會見到，唔好去錯visa application center<br />\n順利搞點既話，大約一個星期拎得，記得check清楚啲資料先好走。"},{"pid":"04c7bb824987e1d6c3ccced8f76a7dfb2911a575","tid":557765,"uid":89417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大概用咗幾多錢</blockquote><br />\n洗左2萬左右掛，冇乜點計，計左可能會好肉赤，最貴係去莫曼斯克果程，啲tour超級貴，差唔多千幾蚊一日"},{"pid":"4660515418735aceb6752caab16c495301c9477e","tid":557765,"uid":89417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lm 7月去莫</blockquote><br />\n去莫斯科？打算去幾多日？"},{"pid":"ea004b6d8a0e81629f507aef3f4b9a55f74715b9","tid":557765,"uid":48762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:15:52.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ed842019ab9fc71fca6ff8a3c3e28b8395c3041a","tid":557765,"uid":31410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:22:34.000Z","msg":"lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20e592ef470148e948e229df166ed7d95fae2e3","tid":557765,"uid":25659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:33:41.000Z","msg":"今個月尾會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8582fc8e08cefc7af7afbd81b97d2be5e1f6d0c","tid":557765,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4660515418735aceb6752caab16c495301c9477e","tid":557765,"uid":89417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lm 7月去莫</blockquote><br />\n去莫斯科？打算去幾多日？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:33:52.000Z","msg":"7日淨莫斯科淨有咩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75778e62526192f5ba419a0e9e45d79a5219128a","tid":557765,"uid":89417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T18:01:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Lm 7月去莫</blockquote><br />\n去莫斯科？打算去幾多日？</blockquote>7日淨莫斯科淨有咩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n莫斯科其實冇乜野睇，3日可以行曬，你可以坐火車去聖彼得堡，4個鐘車程，聖彼得堡多野睇啲，靚啲"},{"pid":"354cf16a8a297515327242250c39f842948f5f01","tid":557765,"uid":127052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T18:14:40.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯啲飛機好似幾危險<br />\n一時時都有意外"},{"pid":"8f70b57a78ef6874b4c119f50329d8b6d2f2ad48","tid":557765,"uid":22632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T18:17:52.000Z","msg":"高汁留名"},{"pid":"2727891617448d0059874376d6f965ae13b74884","tid":557765,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T22:54:23.000Z","msg":"其實就咁睇俄羅斯都幾多連登仔去<br />\n西伯利亞鐵路出完又出<br />\n一d都唔冷門<br />\n<br />\n七月去莫斯科同聖彼德堡睇波<br />\n樓主有無坐過紅箭號？<br />\n<br />\n同埋有無訂馬戲團同劇院教學？"},{"pid":"825deed5f983e246bbddf5a890af438f0a6ec856","tid":557765,"uid":89417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T00:47:35.0